(1, 'c014fb77-3d0c-43e5-918f-5339fa2b1c4d', 'mhn M UP Recruitment 2021: Notification Out For 797 CHO Posts', 'mhn-m-up-recruitment-2021-notification-out-for-797-cho-posts', '2021-07-14', '09:44', '1626248968.png', 'NHM UP Recruitment 2021: Notification Out For 797 CHO Posts', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/article-dashboard/PHP/uploads/NHM-UP-Recruitment-2021.png\" style=\"height:316px; width:500px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>NHM UP has invited online applications for various posts of 797 CHOs or Community Health Officers under the Ayushman Bharat Scheme, Government of Uttar Pradesh envisioned strengthening Sub-Health Centers as Health and Wellness Centers (HWCs). Read the article below to know more about NHM UP Recruitment 2021 like the application process, eligibility criteria, vacancy details, online application link and much more.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">NHM UP Recruitment 2021</span></h2>\n\n<p><strong>NHM UP Recruitment 2021:&nbsp;</strong>The National Health Mission (NHM), Uttar Pradesh has released an official notification inviting applications from eligible Indian citizens on 797 posts of Community Health Officers (CHOs) on its official website @upnrhm.gov.in against Advt No. 2021-22/1722.&nbsp;<strong>The online application process will be started from 28th July 2021 onwards and the last date to apply online is 17th August 2021.&nbsp;</strong>Read the article below for more details about NHM UP Recruitment 2021 regarding the eligibility, application process, selection process and much more.</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">NHM UP Recruitment 2021: Overview</span></h2>\n\n<p>The candidates must go through the table below to understand NHM UP Recruitment 2021.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width:510px\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>NHM UP Recruitment 2021</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Organization Name</strong></td>\n			<td>National Health Mission, Uttar Pradesh (NHM UP)</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Post Name</strong></td>\n			<td>CHO</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Vacancies</strong></td>\n			<td>797 Posts</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Online Application Starts</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>28th July 2021</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Last Date to Apply Online</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>17th August 2021</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Mode Of Application</strong></td>\n			<td>Online</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Category</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.adda247.com/jobs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Govt Jobs</strong></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Advt. No.</strong></td>\n			<td>2021-22/1722</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Official Website</strong></td>\n			<td>www.upnrhm.gov.in</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">NHM UP Notification PDF</span></h2>\n\n<p>The official notification for NHM UP Recruitment 2021 has been already released on the official website @upnrhm.gov.in. The interested candidates can download the detailed notification mentioning all the details regarding eligibility criteria, the application process, and much more regarding NHM UP Recruitment 2021 below.</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">NHM UP Recruitment 2021: Important Dates</span></h2>\n\n<p>All the important dates from the release of official notification for NHM UP Recruitment 2021 till the date of filling form has been given below for the reference purpose to the candidates</p>\n\n<table style=\"width:730px\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>EVENTS</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>DATE</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Notification release Date</td>\n			<td>12th July 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Online Application Start Date</td>\n			<td>28th July 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Last date for applying Online</td>\n			<td>17th August 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Exam date</td>\n			<td>To be announced</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Final Result</td>\n			<td>To be announced</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>NHM UP Vacancy Details</h2>\n\n<p>The Vacancy for NHM UP Recruitment 2021 is given below for a total of 797 posts of CHOs or Community Health Workers. The given table shows the various vacancies in different disciplines.</p>\n\n<table>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Name of the Posts</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>No. of Posts</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>CHO (Community Health Workers)</td>\n			<td>797 Posts</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Total</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>797 Posts</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">NHM UP Eligibility Criteria</span></h2>\n\n<p>Before applying for the various posts above the candidate must go through the eligibility conditions and make sure he/she fulfils them with respect to educational qualification, as well as the age limit for NHM UP Recruitment 2021 which is given below:</p>\n\n<h3>Educational Qualification</h3>\n\n<p>The candidate must have the minimum educational qualifications with respect to the posts of NHM UP CHO which is passed B.Sc. (Nursing) with the integrated curriculum of Certificate in Community Health for Nurses (CCHN)</p>\n\n<p>OR</p>\n\n<p>Post Basic B.Sc. (Nursing) course with the integrated curriculum of Certificate in Community Health for Nurses (CCHN) from recognized Institute or University will be eligible to apply.<br />\nAND</p>\n\n<p>The Candidates must be registered as Nurse and Midwifery from UP Nurses &amp; Midwives Council and have a valid registration certificate at the time of online submission of application.</p>\n\n<h3>Age Limit (as on 17-08-2021)</h3>\n\n<p>The candidates applying must be of a&nbsp;<strong>minimum age of 18 years and maximum age is 35 years.&nbsp;</strong>The age relaxations will be as per guidelines in this regard.</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">NHM UP Online Application Link</span></h2>\n\n<p>The interested and eligible candidates who are willing to apply for the above mentioned various posts have to apply for the same by clicking on the link below to apply online or directly visit the official website @upnrhm.gov.in for the NHM UP Recruitment 2021.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', 'blogs', 'true', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.124 Safari/537.36', 'NHM UP Recruitment 2021: Notification Out For 797 CHO Posts', 'published', 'NHM,UP', 'public', 'mhn M UP Recruitment 2021: Notification Out For 797 CHO Posts', 'http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/read/JOBS/NHM-Category/mhn-m-up-recruitment-2021-notification-out-for-797-cho-posts', 'NHM UP Recruitment 2021: Notification Out For 797 CHO Posts', 'http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/assets/images/uploads/1626248968.png', 'Wed, 14 Jul 2021 13:19:28 +0530', 'Wed, 14 Jul 2021 13:19:28 +0530', '9514003d-8529-4176-9b69-a3f8b6bff1bf'),
