(11, 'b3b6bea2-0c31-4644-813a-4a5cdc939b0c', 'IBPS Clerk Salary 2021: Detailed IBPS Clerk In hand, Job Profile & Promotions', 'ibps-clerk-salary-2021-detailed-ibps-clerk-in-hand-job-profile-promotions', '2021-07-15', '10:36', '1626338467.png', 'IBPS Clerk Salary 2021: Detailed IBPS Clerk In hand, Job Profile & Promotions', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/article-dashboard/PHP/uploads/IBPS-Clerk-Salary-min.png\" style=\"height:315px; width:500px\" /></p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">BPS Clerk Salary 2021</span></h2>\n\n<p><strong>IBPS Clerk Salary 2021:</strong>&nbsp;The Institute of Banking Personnel Selection (IBPS) is the conducting body for the recruitment of the IBPS Clerks. With the release of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.adda247.com/jobs/ibps-clerk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>IBPS Clerk Notification</strong></a>&nbsp;for 2021, there is a curiosity among the candidates regarding the salary, perks, and allowances.</p>\n\n<p>This article below has detailed the candidates with the IBPS Clerk Job Profile, including Salary In hand, Pay Scale, Allowances, Job Profile &amp; Promotions. Read further for complete details.</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">IBPS Clerk Salary 2021: Pay Scale</span></h2>\n\n<p><strong>IBPS Clerk Salary&nbsp;</strong>is the sum of Basic Pay and other Allowances like HRA (House Rent Allowance and Dearness allowances etc.) The first Basic Pay for IBPS Clerk 2021 is Rs 11,765.<br />\nIBPS Clerk Payscale is<strong>&nbsp;11765-655/3- 13730-815/3- 16175-980/4- 20095-1145/7- 28110-2120/1- 30230/1310-1- 31540.</strong><br />\nThis is not very easy to understand so we have made it more clear and easy to understand through the table below. While basically, that means the minimum Basic Pay for IBPS Clerk is Rs 11,765 while the maximum is Rs 31540.</p>\n\n<table>\n	<thead>\n		<tr>\n			<th>Basic Pay</th>\n			<th>Amount</th>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Initial Basic Pay</td>\n			<td>Rs 11,765, with a yearly increment of Rs 655 for three years</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Basic Pay after 3 years</td>\n			<td>Rs 13730, with a yearly increment of Rs 815 for the next three years</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Basic Pay after the next 3 years</td>\n			<td>Rs 16175, with a yearly increment of Rs 980 for the next four years</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Basic Pay after the next 4 years</td>\n			<td>Rs 20095, with a yearly increment of Rs 1145 for the next 7 years</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Basic Pay after the next 7 years</td>\n			<td>Rs 28110, with a yearly increment of Rs 2120 for the next year</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Basic Pay after the next 1 year</td>\n			<td>Rs 30230, with a yearly increment of Rs 1310 for the next year</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Basic Pay after next year 1 year</td>\n			<td>&nbsp;Rs 31540 (maximum Basic Pay)</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">IBPS Clerk Salary: Allowances</span></h2>\n\n<p><strong>IBPS Clerk Salary Allowances are quite lucrative.</strong>&nbsp;There are several allowances provided to a clerk through IBPS. These allowances depend on various factors that may include the location of posting, how the branch is progressing and some other factors. The various types of allowances provided to the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.careerpower.in/ibps-clerk-salary.html\"><strong>IBPS Clerk</strong>&nbsp;</a>are listed below:</p>\n\n<table style=\"width:954px\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Special Allowance</strong></td>\n			<td>Rs 1561</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Dearness Allowance (DA)</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>DA is 4 per cent of the IBPS Clerk Basic Pay.</li>\n				<li>DA depends on the CPI and is revised quarterly, i.e. after every three months.</li>\n				<li>The starting DA would be Rs 7073</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>House Rent Allowance (HRA)</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<ul>\n				<li>The HRA depends on the location of the posting.</li>\n				<li>The HRA remains between 6.5% to 8.5% depending upon the location of the posting.</li>\n			</ul>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Travel Allowance (TA)</strong></td>\n			<td>Expenses on official tours and travels will be reimbursed by the bank.</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Medical Allowance (MA)</strong></td>\n			<td>This is paid once a year. For IBPS Clerks, the amount is fixed at Rs 2000/- annually.</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', 'blogs', 'true', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.124 Safari/537.36', 'IBPS Clerk Salary 2021: Detailed IBPS Clerk In hand, Job Profile & Promotions', 'published', 'ibps,salary', 'public', 'IBPS Clerk Salary 2021: Detailed IBPS Clerk In hand, Job Profile & Promotions', 'http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/read/IBPS-Clerk-Exam/IBPS-Clerk-Salary/ibps-clerk-salary-2021-detailed-ibps-clerk-in-hand-job-profile-promotions', 'IBPS Clerk Salary 2021: Detailed IBPS Clerk In hand, Job Profile & Promotions', 'http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/assets/images/uploads/1626338467.png', 'Thu, 15 Jul 2021 14:11:06 +0530', 'Thu, 15 Jul 2021 14:11:06 +0530', '9514003d-8529-4176-9b69-a3f8b6bff1bf'),
(12, 'fece272d-46a1-4418-a47e-4c5053a69cde', 'PSPCL Recruitment Notification', 'pspcl-recruitment-notification', '2021-07-16', '07:52', '1626414958.png', 'PSPCL Recruitment Notification', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Punjab State Power Corporation Limited (PSPCL) has invited eligible candidates for 2632 Technical and Non-Technical posts. The recruitment will be conducted for posts including Assistant Lineman, Clerk, Revenue Accountant, Junior Engineer/ Electrical, Assistant Sub Station Attendant. Go through the below article for eligibility, vacancy distribution, exam pattern, online application link and more.</p>\n\n<p>Table of Contents</p>\n\n<h2>PSPCL Recruitment 2021</h2>\n\n<p><strong>PSPCL Recruitment 2021</strong>: Punjab State Power Corporation Limited (PSPCL) had released an official notification announcing 2632 vacancies of Technical and Non-Technical posts on its official website @pspcl.in on 21st May 2021. The recruitment will be conducted for Assistant Lineman (AL), Clerk, Revenue Accountant, Junior Engineer/ Electrical, Assistant Sub Station Attendant (ASSA) posts.&nbsp;<strong>The online registration process for PSTCL Various Vacancies has been again extended till 28th July 2021</strong><strong>.&nbsp;</strong>The interested candidates are advised to go through the below article for more information.</p>\n\n<h2>PSPCL Recruitment 2021: Highlights</h2>\n\n<table>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>PSPCL Recruitment 2021 Notification</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Organization Name</strong></td>\n			<td>Punjab State Power Corporation Limited (PSPCL)</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Post Name</strong></td>\n			<td>Assistant Lineman, Clerk, Revenue Accountant, Junior Engineer/ Electrical, Assistant SubStation Attendant</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Vacancies</strong></td>\n			<td>2632</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Online Application Starts</strong></td>\n			<td><del>31st May 2021</del>&nbsp;<del>10th June 2021</del