(20, '6ced75f7-d1fa-4226-a209-395ae392a007', 'MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: For 279 Fireman, Station Fire Officer & Other Posts', 'mc-chandigarh-recruitment-2021-for-279-fireman-station-fire-officer-other-posts', '2021-07-14', '13:08', '1626261431.png', 'MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: For 279 Fireman, Station Fire Officer & Other Posts', '<h1><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/article-dashboard/PHP/uploads/Chandigarh-MC-Recruitment-2021.png\" style=\"height:189px; width:300px\" /></h1>\n\n<p>Chandigarh Municipal Corporation has invited online applications from eligible Indian citizens for 279 various posts that include Station Fire Officer, Fireman, and driver posts. Read the article below to know more about MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021 like the application process, eligibility criteria, vacancy details, online application link and much more.</p>\n\n<p>Table of Contents</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021</span></h2>\n\n<p><strong>MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021:&nbsp;</strong>MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021, has released an official notification inviting online applications from eligible Indian citizens on 279 various posts mentioned below on its official website @mcchandigarh.gov.in.&nbsp;<strong>The online application process will be started from 12th July 2021 and the last date to apply online is 30th July 2021.&nbsp;</strong>Read the article below for more details about MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021 regarding the eligibility, application process, selection process and much more.</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: Overview</span></h2>\n\n<p>The candidates must go through the table below to understand MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021.</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:510px\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Organization Name</strong></td>\n			<td>Chandigarh Municipal Corporation</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Post Name</strong></td>\n			<td>Various Posts</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Vacancies</strong></td>\n			<td>279</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Online Application Starts</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>12th July 2021</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Last Date to Apply Online</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>30th July 2021</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Mode Of Application</strong></td>\n			<td>Online</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Category</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.adda247.com/jobs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Govt Jobs</strong></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Job Location</strong></td>\n			<td>Punjab, Chandigarh</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Official Website</strong></td>\n			<td>www.mcchandigarh.gov.in</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">MC Chandigarh Notification PDF</span></h2>\n\n<p>The official notification for MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021 has been already released on the official website @mcchandigarh.gov.in. The interested candidates can download the detailed notification mentioning all the details regarding eligibility criteria, the application process, and much more regarding MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021 below.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"simple-button-plugin\" href=\"https://www.adda247.com/jobs/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06193836/Chandigarh-MC-Job-notification-2021.pdf\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(255, 85, 33); border: 1px solid rgb(255, 85, 33); padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; text-decoration: none !important;\" target=\"_blank\">MC CHANDIGARH NOTIFICATION PDF</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"color:#e67e22\">MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: Important Dates</span></h2>\n\n<p>All the important dates from the release of official notification for MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021 till the date of filling form has been given below for the reference purpose to the candidates</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:730px\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>EVENTS</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>DATE</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Notification release Date</td>\n			<td>5th July 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Application Start Date</td>\n			<td>12th July 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Application Last Date</td>\n			<td>30th July 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Last date of submitting the application fee</td>\n			<td>03rd August 2021</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Exam Date</td>\n			<td>To be announced</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>MC Chandigarh Vacancy Details</h2>\n\n<p>The Vacancy Distribution of MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021 is given below for a total of 279 vacancies of Station Fire Officer, Fireman, and driver.</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:564px\">\n	<thead>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Name of the Posts</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>No. of posts</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Station Fire Officer</td>\n			<td>03 Posts</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Fire Man</td>\n			<td>220 Posts</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Driver</td>\n			<td>56 Posts</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Total</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>279 Posts</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', 'blogs', 'true', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/92.0.4515.107 Safari/537.36', 'MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: For 279 Fireman, Station Fire Officer & Other Posts', 'preview', 'exams blogs', 'public', 'MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: For 279 Fireman, Station Fire Officer & Other Posts', 'http://localhost:8080/blog-cms-admin/read-cat/jobs/mc-chandigarh-recruitment-2021-for-279-fireman-station-fire-officer-other-posts', 'MC Chandigarh Recruitment 2021: For 279 Fireman, Station Fire Officer & Other Posts', 'http://localhost:808